>The S-box stuff has always been available on arisia.xerox.com, now known
>as beta.xerox.com, in directory /pub/hash.

Furthermore (I haven't checked this directory and it may contain
the documents), the S boxes in question are derived from the 30 or more year
old RAND random number tables, in such a way that "tampering" with these
boxes, to introduce trapdoors, is essetially ruled out.

